pyMeme is the official Python port of iMeme, a meme generator for Mac OS X.

pyMeme has been tested on Windows and Mac OS X but should also work on Linux.

http://www.michaelfogleman.com/imeme/

* Over 50 built-in templates.
* Enter your own header and footer text.
* Adjustable text size and alignment.
* Use your own images.
* Save as JPG.
* Works on Windows XP and up.
